Hello Folks,

I would like to do technical SEO audit for the website ~1000 pages for free of charge. The preferred websites will be those which can implement the recommended changes quicker with the help of their developers and can share GSC access to check improvements.

Why do I do it for free? Ans.: I have new tool and want to explore it. That's it.

Feel free to DM.

Looking forward.

Sincerely,
Shahid Abbasi
